    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "A planned or scheduled event that has a specific purpose and brings together a group of people to participate in activities, celebrations, or shared experiences."
  }, {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Acontecimiento planificado o programado que tiene un propósito específico y reúne a un grupo de personas para participar en actividades, celebraciones o experiencias compartidas."
